        "commandline": "pwsh.exe -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command \"cd '$PROFILE/../../../Documents/GitHub/tradeadviser/server/app/frontend'; Clear-Host; Write-Host '⚛️  Frontend (React)' -ForegroundColor Green; Write-Host 'Run: npm run dev (http://localhost:5173)'; Write-Host ''; pwsh.exe\"",
